{"tid":340561,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我開24小時Minecraft有冇人會玩？（只限正版）","createTime":"2017-07-30T05:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T10:09:29.000Z","uid":19657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb029332466ef7b57ca519bf1f992883fa77a039","tid":340561,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"買官方Server，真係可以24小時無間斷開足半年<br />\n370蚊我預咗包底，如果你喜歡可以一人夾返十蚊廿蚊<br />\n真係只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7ov5z4cn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7ov5z4cn&h=4957a3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要買Server，其實香港地大家都忙返工返學<br />\n下下要靠人開Server根本玩唔到幾多<br />\n<br />\n好純淨，純到咩程度，冇Mod、冇插件、冇買地<br />\n我當你地係Friend咁一齊玩，所以只靠正版保持質素<br />\n<br />\n有咩目的，最緊要大家Enjoy一齊玩，一齊揾達地方起屋<br />\n起起下變咗條村之後，可能有人想開新地方咁咪轉地方<br />\n又或者你有咩諗法，起個城堡；起下地鐵；整下花海都得<br />\n<br />\n有幾點想問／講你地知：<br />\n1.想要生存定創造？<br />\n2.同一時間只可以有10幾人online，所以其實好少人，唔洗驚畀人冷落，但同時你唔可以單機。（但玩過人地Ser一定知，其實好少10個人同時online）<br />\n3.一定要入Skype Group<br />\n<br />\n想玩嘅PM我，睇下夠唔夠人搞唔搞得成"},{"pid":"0c7d60db57730f3dc366c36e38703278b2633051","tid":340561,"uid":19657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"仆街，PM條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ⋯⋯"},{"pid":"a0d73d5eedb8dde12c08806bd7cee50870fad607","tid":340561,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"Pmed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec0f1f7cd79a045be9087d37e1f769a6a23ccec","tid":340561,"uid":59632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"92c57c6574833d6c3298dff392750723d6b45793","tid":340561,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"我有興趣"},{"pid":"a2784025f78cc3b6e46caa612eb12ac96f9de7bb","tid"